{"id":2215,"date":"2012-11-15T05:50:56","date_gmt":"2012-11-15T11:50:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/lupus_foundation_of_america.php"},"modified":"2012-11-15T05:50:56","modified_gmt":"2012-11-15T11:50:56","slug":"lupus_foundation_of_america","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/lupus_foundation_of_america.php","title":{"rendered":"Lupus Foundation of America"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/lupus_foa_logo.gif\" alt=\"Lupus Foundation of America Logo, Before and After\" \/><\/p>\n<p><strong>About: <\/strong> (Est. 1977) &#8220;The <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lupus.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lupus Foundation of America<\/a> is the only national force devoted to solving the mystery of lupus, one of the world&#8217;s cruelest, most unpredictable and devastating diseases, while giving caring support to those who suffer from its brutal impact.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Design by:<\/strong> <a href=\"http:\/\/siegelvisioncorp.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Siegelvision<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Ed.&#8217;s Notes:<\/strong> I get the concept, I just wish the execution were competent. The result is painfully amateurish.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Relevant links:<\/strong> <a href=\"http:\/\/www.lupus.org\/webmodules\/webarticlesnet\/templates\/new_empty.aspx?articleid=4805&#038;zoneid=99\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Press release<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Select quote:<\/strong> &#8220;The organization&#8217;s new positioning strategy, messages, and tag line &mdash; <em>Help Us Solve the Cruel Mystery<\/em> &mdash; were created in collaboration with the New York branding team Siegelvision, headed by brand guru Alan Siegel. The riveting phrase &#8220;cruel mystery&#8221; inspired the Siegelvision team to create the new Lupus Foundation of America logo which features a strikingly positioned question mark in place of the letter &#8220;P&#8221; in the word lupus.&#8221;<\/p><!--more--><p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/lupus_foa_bus.jpg\" alt=\"Lupus Foundation of America\" width=\"574\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"caption\">&#8220;The centerpiece of the education effort is a 45-foot bus with eight interactive exhibits and displays, where visitors can experience what it is like to live with lupus, reinforcing the urgent need to end the disease&#8217;s brutal impact.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p class=\"bottom\">Thanks to Colette Ford for the tip.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<script type=\"text\/javascript\" src=\"swfobject.js\"><\/script>\n<script type=\"text\/javascript\">\n\t<!--\n\tfunction pollSystemObj()\n\t{\n\t\tvar now = new Date();\n\t\tvar hour = now.getHours();\n\t\tvar minute = now.getMinutes();\n\t\tvar second = now.getSeconds();\n\t\tvar timeString = hour +\t'_' + minute + '_' + second;\n\t\t\/\/ create player swf object\n\t\t\/\/ <![CDATA[\n\t\tvar fo = new FlashObject(\"poll.swf?xml=poll_121115_b_config_01.xml&#038;xyz=poll_121115_b_votes_01.xml&#038;timeString\", \"poll\", \"574\", \"235\", 7);\n\t\tfo.write(\"pollDiv1\");\n\t\t\/\/ ]]&gt;\n\t}\n\t-->\n<\/script>\n<!--START DATA TABLE-->\n<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_voting_start.gif\" alt=\"Voting Begins\" \/>\n<table class=\"table\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n\t<tr valign=\"top\">\n        <!--VOTE CONCEPT-->\n\t\t<td class=\"table_col\">\n\t\t\t<div id = \"pollDiv1\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/td>\n\t<\/tr>\n<\/table>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/divider_voting_end.gif\" alt=\"Voting Ends\" \/>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorde